 ${shlibs:Depends},
 librefs13 (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: read-only ReFS library (development)
 librefs provides a read-only interface for interacting with the ReFS filesystem
 filesystem used by recent versions of Microsoft Windows.
 .
 This package contains the development files.

