Package: refs-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms (>> 2.1.1.2-5),
         file,
         libc6-dev | libc-dev,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${perl:Depends}
Recommends: refsprogs (>= ${source:Version}), ${linux:Recommends}
Provides: refs-modules
Description: ReFS filesystem kernel modules for Linux
 refs-dkms uses DKMS to dynamically build a Linux kernel module to provide
 native read-only support for the ReFS filesystem used by recent versions of
 Microsoft Windows.
